Class MultimediaResource

java.lang.Object
app.tracktune.model.resource.Resource
app.tracktune.model.resource.MultimediaResource
public class MultimediaResource extends Resource
Represents a multimedia resource associated with a track and user. Extends the base Resource class by adding location and resource date.

    • MultimediaResource

      public MultimediaResource(Integer id, ResourceTypeEnum type, byte[] data, Timestamp creationDate, boolean isMultimedia, String location, Date resourceDate, boolean isAuthor, int trackID, int userID)
      Constructs a MultimediaResource with a specified ID.
      Parameters:
      id - the unique identifier of the resource, can be null for new entities
      type - the type of the resource (see ResourceTypeEnum)
      data - the binary data of the resource
      creationDate - the timestamp when the resource was created
      isMultimedia - flag indicating if the resource is multimedia
      location - the location/path of the multimedia resource
      resourceDate - the date associated with the resource (e.g., creation or capture date)
      isAuthor - flag indicating if the resource is related to an author
      trackID - the ID of the track this resource is linked to
      userID - the ID of the user who owns or created the resource
